  m_text: 'This game was developed in collaboration with young game jammers as part
    of the EPIC-WE project.


    EPIC-WE is an EU-funded initiative that brings
    together young creatives, cultural institutions, and game industry professionals
    to explore and express cultural values through game-making.

    Through a series
    of game jams, participants designed and developed unique experiences reflecting
    their perspectives on heritage, society, and the future.

'
